            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Fraolmus">Fraolmi</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Winizo">Winizio</name></persName> per hanc
                        cartula pro anime mee remedium dispone e conferma per dopo la sua morte
                        nella potestate della figlia <persName key="#Abbesses"><name ref="Euphemia"
                                >Eufemia</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbesses">badessa</rs>, di <persName><name ref="Ughicio"
                                >Ughiccione</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Rainerius"
                                >Ranieri</name></persName>, di <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Sigitius">Sizio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs> figlio del <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notaio</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Sigenulfus">Sighinolfo</name></persName>,
                        del <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Lampertus">Lamberto</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Homodeus">Omodei</name></persName>, omnibus
                        chasis et chassinis seo chasalinis sive <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiis</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Forests">silvis et buschareis</rs> simulque terris et rebus
                        poste in locho <placeName ref="#places/170">Decimo</placeName> et im locho
                            <placeName ref="#places/3116">Versilia</placeName> et im locho
                            <placeName ref="#places/3117">Curbaria</placeName> et im locho
                            <placeName ref="#places/3115">Fabbiano</placeName> et im locho
                            <placeName ref="#places/3118">Mamtiano</placeName> et im locho
                            <placeName ref="#places/3119">Nocche</placeName>, com omnibus rebus tam
                            <rs key="#Demesnes">domnichatas</rs> quam massariciis, sive aldonariciis
                        et tributariis, che a lui spettano in quei luoghi, una cum tribus personis:
                            <persName key="#Slave"><name ref="Ughicio"
                            >Ughiccione</name></persName> figlio <rs key="#Clerical_concubinage">di
                                <persName key="#Clerical_concubinage"><name ref="Bonitia"
                                    >Bonizia</name></persName></rs>, <persName key="#Slave"
                                ><name ref="Citta">Citta</name></persName> figlia <rs
                            key="#Clerical_concubinage">della <persName key="#Clerical_concubinage"
                                >fu <name ref="Berta">Berta</name></persName></rs>, <persName
                            key="#Slave"><name ref="Eva">Eva</name></persName> figlia di
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardus">Gherardo</name></persName>, <rs
                            key="#Slave_labour">servo et ancille</rs> mee una cum omni eorum
                        actionem et pertinentiis. Stabilisce che alla sua morte i suddetti beni
                        apparterranno a quello dei donatari che avr√† in mano la presente iudicati
                        cartula. Chiede al <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Copyist #Notary"><name ref="Sigenulfus"
                                >Sighinolfo</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum in
                        suprascripto locho Fabbiano. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs>
                        sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Cunitius"
                            >Cunizio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Clerical_concubinage">della <persName key="#Clerical_concubinage"
                                >fu <name ref="Alsinda">Alsinda</name></persName></rs>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Sigefredus">Sighifridi</name></persName> di
                                <persName><name ref="Cunitius">Cunizio</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Paganuccius">Paganuccio</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Cappatino">Cappatino</name></persName>. <rs
                            key="#Copyist">Copiatore</rs>: Sighinolfo notarius dom. imp, che scrisse
                        l'originale. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Lambertus">Lamberto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius dom. imp</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rodulfus">Rodolfo</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
